{"id":231807972,"title":"【調酒】自己調弱弱的Mojito","content":"先恭喜品酒版開版\n各路酒鬼終於有個討論的專屬空間\n\n說的調酒\n當然要提到mojito\nhttps://i.imgur.com/yucOxth.jpg\n<圖片取自網路>\n\nmojito是一種傳統的古巴調酒\n由蘭姆酒、白砂糖、青檸汁、蘇打水和薄荷調製而成\n從一大堆冰塊跟薄荷就可以知道\n他是一杯比較清爽的酒\n適合酒吧新手點喔喔\n\nps. mojito好像是西班牙語\n所以念法上j要發[h]的音\n想當初第一次點竟然用英文唸他\n真尷尬QQ\n\n最後附上自己調的mojito\nhttps://i.imgur.com/hnl7bYI.jpg\n感覺讓人食慾大減😂\n因為我喜歡口味重一點\n所以薄荷跟蘭姆酒都加很多\n\n話說台灣不好買薄荷\n找了好久最後靈機一動\n去建國花市買\n一大盆才100哦\n然後又自己繁殖了一大堆\n下次可以來寫一篇薄荷栽種教學😆","excerpt":"先恭喜品酒版開版，各路酒鬼終於有個討論的專屬空間，說的調酒，當然要提到mojito，<圖片取自網路>，mojito是一種傳統的古巴調酒，由蘭姆酒、白砂糖、青檸汁、蘇打水和薄荷調製而成，從一大堆冰塊跟薄","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-06T18:15:03.466Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-06T18:15:03.466Z","commentCount":25,"likeCount":58,"tags":[],"topics":["調酒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"情趣工坊","department":"nickname1013","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":58}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxth.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/hnl7bYI.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"16e03d71-c4f6-4532-9ef8-95f8e63a7d77","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxthl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxthl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxthl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-06T18:15:03.466Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-06T18:15:03.466Z"},{"id":"16e03d71-c4f6-4532-9ef8-95f8e63a7d77","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxth.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/yucOxth","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yucOxthl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-06T18:15:03.466Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-06T18:1